sequenceDiagram
    participant Jogador
    participant Input as InputHandler
    participant Cmd as Command
    participant Rules as GameRules
    participant Turn as TurnManager
    participant AI as EnemyAI
    participant Render as SadConsoleRenderer
    Jogador->>Input: Pressiona tecla
    Input->>Cmd: Cria MoveCommand
    Cmd->>Rules: Execute(world)
    Rules->>Rules: Valida colisao/combate
    Rules->>Turn: Consome turno do jogador
    Turn->>AI: Processa inimigos
    AI->>Rules: Move/ataca/interage
    Rules->>Render: Estado atualizado
    Render->>Jogador: Desenha mapa e UI
